      "content": "but that's just what people say to be nice. if you actually look at the numbers and how much we're struggling, it's just math. they would get more help, more stability, and they wouldn't have to watch me fail every single day. it's almost like a sacrifice. wouldn't it be more selfless to just... step out of the way?",
